WEBVTT

00:05.019 --> 00:07.487
<i>[Female Dispatcher]
KDK-12, come in. KDK-12.</i>

00:07.521 --> 00:09.222
KDK-12.

00:09.256 --> 00:12.725
<i>Hey, Bobby, need you to look in on Mrs.
Peyketewa.</i>

00:12.760 --> 00:13.827
She all right?

00:13.861 --> 00:15.962
<i>Her daughter called
from California,</i>

00:15.996 --> 00:17.497
<i>she hasn't heard
from her in a while,</i>

00:17.531 --> 00:19.132
<i>kind of worried.</i>

00:19.166 --> 00:20.633
Will do.

